'''班加羅爾·曼朱納特·拉胡爾·巴拉德瓦吉'''（{{lang-en|Bangalore Manjunath Rahul Bharadwaj}}，{{bd|2000年|4月18日|||catIdx=}}），通常簡稱'''B·M·拉胡爾·巴拉德瓦吉'''（{{lang|en|B. M. Rahul Bharadwaj}}），[[印度|印度]]男子[[羽球|羽球]]運動員。

== 簡歷 ==
B·M·拉胡爾·巴拉德瓦吉出生自[[卡納塔克邦|卡納塔克邦]][[邦加羅爾|邦加羅爾]]，從小在羽球名宿[[普拉卡什·帕都恭|普拉卡什·帕都恭]]開設的羽球學院接受訓練<ref>{{cite news|title=Rahul Bharadwaj: On the rise|url=https://www.newindianexpress.com/cities/bengaluru/2013/feb/14/rahul-bharadwaj-on-the-rise-450238.html|newspaper=The New Indian Express|date=2013-02-14|accessdate=2021-04-05|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210405084023/https://www.newindianexpress.com/cities/bengaluru/2013/feb/14/rahul-bharadwaj-on-the-rise-450238.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Rahul Bhardwaj beat George in tiring semifinal|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/badminton/rahul-bhardwaj-beat-george-in-tiring-semifinal/articleshow/60345476.cms|newspaper=[[印度時報|印度時報]]|date=2017-09-03|accessdate=2021-04-05|language=en|archive-date=2017-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924211820/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/badminton/rahul-bhardwaj-beat-george-in-tiring-semifinal/articleshow/60345476.cms}}</ref>。2019年，巴拉德瓦吉在[[2019年烏干達羽毛球國際賽|烏干達國際賽]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Rahul wins Uganda International Title|url=https://www.ppba.in/rahul-wins-uganda-international-title.html|website=ppba.in|publisher=Prakash Padukone Badminton Academy|date=2019-02-25|accessdate=2021-04-05|language=en|archive-date=2020-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200511233015/https://www.ppba.in/rahul-wins-uganda-international-title.html}}</ref>、[[2019年肯亞羽毛球國際賽|肯亞國際賽]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Rahul wins Kenya Open Future Series|url=https://sportstar.thehindu.com/badminton/rahul-bharadwaj-kenya-open-future-series/article26423669.ece|newspaper=[[印度報|印度報]]|date=2019-03-03|accessdate=2021-04-05|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927204717/https://sportstar.thehindu.com/badminton/rahul-bharadwaj-kenya-open-future-series/article26423669.ece}}</ref>和[[2019年克羅地亞羽毛球國際賽|克羅埃西亞國際賽]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Croatian International badminton: BM Rahul clinches men’s singles title, Tanvi Lad loses in final|url=https://scroll.in/field/920835/croatian-international-badminton-bm-rahul-clinches-mens-singles-title-tanvi-lad-loses-in-final|website=Scroll.in|date=2019-04-21|accessdate=2021-04-05|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108002632/https://scroll.in/field/920835/croatian-international-badminton-bm-rahul-clinches-mens-singles-title-tanvi-lad-loses-in-final}}</ref>接連奪下男子單打冠軍。

